<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3778766>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Libitia bipunctata Sørensen, 1932, ♂ (ICN-AO 1040), habitus. A. Dorsal view. B. Dorsal view, panoramic. C. Frontal view. D. Lateral right view. E–F. Right femur IV, dorsal and ventral view, respectively. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3778766/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3778768>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Libitia bipunctata Sørensen, 1932, variation of spot pattern on dorsal scutum. A–D. ♂♂. A. IAvH-I-67. B. ICN-AO 468. C. ICN-AO 419. D. IAvH-I-87. E–H. ♀♀. E. IAvH-I-76. F–H. UNAL- AO 420. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3778768/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3778777>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Libitia cordata (Gervais, 1844), variation of spot pattern on dorsal scutum. A–D. ♂♂. A. ICN-AO 1040. B. ICN-AO 421. C. ICN-AO 1040. D. ICN-AO 1040. E–H. ♀♀. E–F. ICN-AO 421. G–H. ICN-AO 1040. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3778777/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3778775>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Libitia cordata (Gervais, 1844), ♂ (ICN-AO 1040), habitus. A. Dorsal view. B. Dorsal view, panoramic. C. Frontal view. D. Lateral right view. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3778775/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3778783>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Libitia gandalf sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (IAvH-I-69), habitus. A. Dorsal view. B. Dorsal view, anterior margin of carapace. C. Dorsal view, panoramic. D. Frontal view. E. Right lateral view. F–G. Right femur IV, dorsal and ventral view, respectively. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3778783/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3778772>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Libitia bipunctata Sørensen, 1932, ♂ (ICN-AO 419), distal part of penis. A. Dorsal view B. Right lateral view. C. Ventral view, macrosetae colorised and numbered. D. Stylus, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–C = 50 μm; D = 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3778772/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

